on notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/zcorpan/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/zcorpan\">@zcorpan</a> <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/smaug----/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/smaug----\">@smaug----</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Other information</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">This is developed as part of cross-document view-transitions, but we're sending separate RFPs for  the sub-features that can work outside the context of view-transitions, to make sure we're all on the same page.</p>",
