okers proposal</a>.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">See also, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1909491215\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/whatwg/html/issues/9776\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/whatwg/html/issues/9776/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/whatwg/html/issues/9776\">whatwg/html#9776</a>.</p>",
